OL,3,CTram and rail passengers face a week
OL,4,Cof disruption as strikes get underway
OL,6,FRail and tram passengers face a week
OL,7,Fof disruption because of strikes which
OL,8,Fwill lead to some parts of the country
OL,9,Fhaving no trains on days of industrial
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,FMembers of the train drivers' union
OL,13,FAslef at 16 operators will launch a
OL,14,Fsix-day ban on overtime on Monday,
OL,15,Fwhich is expected to cause short-
OL,16,Fnotice cancellations.
OL,18,FThey will also stage three, one-day
OL,19,Fstrikes across different operators
OL,20,Fbetween May 7 and 9, as part of a long
OL,21,Frunning dispute over pay.
