OL,6,F"We can only apologise to our
OL,7,Fcustomers for this wholly unnecessary
OL,8,Fstrike action called by the Aslef
OL,9,Fleadership which will sadly disrupt
OL,10,Fjourneys once again.
OL,12,F"It will also inflict further damage
OL,13,Fon an industry that is receiving up to
OL,14,Fan additional #54 million a week in
OL,15,Ftaxpayer cash to keep services
OL,16,Frunning, following the Covid downturn."
