OL,6,FDepartment for Transport spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Transport Secretary and
OL,8,FRail Minister have already facilitated
OL,9,Fa pay offer that would take train
OL,10,Fdrivers' average salaries up to
OL,11,F#65,000 ` almost twice the UK average
OL,12,Fsalary.J"Aslef are the only union left
OL,13,Fstriking after the government oversaw
OL,14,Fdeals with all the other unions.
OL,15,F"Instead of causing passengers
OL,16,Fdisruption, they should put this offer
OL,17,Fto their members and work with
OL,18,Findustry to end this dispute."
